{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, Schindler's factory-- let me tell you a little bit about Schindler.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came to Poland, like many other Nazis, to seek fortune.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took over a pots and pans factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was a good item for a black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was a Jewish factory, who he took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In order to make more money and increase production, he had enough influence to bribe some Nazis to give him more people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And actually, he established a subcamp of this concentration camp, Krakau-Plaszow, because he fenced if off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were watchtowers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The SS people were watching us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, in the factory, they never had anything to do with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We worked 12 hours a day, two shifts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "However, we had more food, better food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had better hygiene condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You could go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You can wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You could do something after your working hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just to give you one example what happened, that because this was a subcamp of the concentration camp, Krakau-Plaszow, every once in a while a few Nazis used to come for inspections, so-called inspections.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Actually, I think they came to be entertained by Schindler, because Schindler had always plenty of liquor, booze, and food, and so to be entertained.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "However, they were walking around a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one of the men, not knowing that the Nazis are around, left his barrack in order to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And walking through, one off the Nazis spotted him and he ordered him to lay down on the ground.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He took his revolver out and was ready to shoot him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Schindler was around and he noticed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He grabbed the Nazi by the arm and said to him, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I will give you a bottle of whiskey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Let the man go.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
